def print_info(self): #print all nodes info print 'Nodes information:' print 'Number of nodes: %s' % len(self.nodes) for node in self.node_dict.keys(): print str(node), ',', self.node_dict[node]
#print all edges info print 'Edges information' print 'Number of edges: %s' % len(self.edges) for edge in self.edge_dict.keys(): print edge.label, ',', self.edge_dict[edge]
